                        </p>


                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-6 footer-links">
                        <h4> <i class="ion-ios-email-outline"></i>  Email</h4>
                        <p> sticollegesjdm@gamil.com </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 footer-info">
                        <h4><i class="ion-ios-telephone-outline"></i>  Phone</h4>
                        <p> (044) 761 6017 </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="https://twitter.com/sticollege" class="twitter"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sjdelmonte.sti.edu" class="facebook"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="copyright">
                &copy; Copyright <strong>STI College San Jose Del Monte Online Monitoring</strong>. All Rights Reserved 2021-2022
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer><!-- #footer -->
